Define function sum_all that takes rest numbers and returns nothing.
    Create total = 0.
    For each item in numbers
        Set total to total + item.
    End
    Display total.
End function.

Call sum_all with 1 and 2 and 3.
Call sum_all with 10 and 20.
Call sum_all.

Define function greet_all that takes text greeting and rest names and returns nothing.
    For each name in names
        Display greeting + " " + name.
    End
End function.

Call greet_all with "Hello" and "Alice" and "Bob" and "Charlie".
